Her poke with her Q is amazing. I was able to hold of a Verus and Morgana Solo bot for 10 mins thanks to that Q and Cait being afk.

That Q has great wave clear. The silence has great zoning. I like the squishier Soraka gives more counter play then being the uncilable healer that gives infant mana and can silence people.
